high_descs: Walk over to the kitchen sink that is in the kitchen island.
Pick up the metal fork out of the sink basin.
Look down into the sink.
Put the metal fork in the green cup that is in the sink.
Pick up the green cup with the metal fork in it.
Turn right and walk forward, then turn right and walk up to the counter.
Put the green cup with the fork in it on the counter in front of the loaf of bread.
anns.task_desc: Put a green cup with a fork in it on the counter.

high_descs: Go ahead until reach counter with coffee maker.  Turn left until reach sink on left.  Turn left to face sink.
Pick up fork from sink, behind tomato.
Face sink in front of you.
Place fork in green mug in front part of sink.
Pick up fork and mug from sink.
Turn around, face counter over dishwasher.
Put mug and fork on counter in front of bread.
anns.task_desc: Move fork into mug, move both on counter.

high_descs: Turn to the right, take a couple steps, turn to the left
Head across the kitchen to the sink
Take the fork out of the sink
Put the fork in the green cup
Take the green cup out of the sink
Turn around, face the counter
Put the green cup on the counter
anns.task_desc: Put the fork in the green cup, put the cup on the counter
